snippet.title: AI War 2: Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Early Access coming October 15th!  Wishlist now on Steam to get notified: https://store.steampowered.com/app/573410

Or backerkit if you want to play right away: https://aiwar2.backerkit.com/hosted_preorders

Thanks for all your support of the game!
